jcolibri.connector.databaseutils
Class GenericUserType

java.lang.Object
  jcolibri.connector.databaseutils.GenericUserType
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.hibernate.usertype.ParameterizedType, org.hibernate.usertype.UserType
public class GenericUserType
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.hibernate.usertype.UserType, org.hibernate.usertype.ParameterizedType

Class that allows to use any jcolibri.connector.TypeAdaptor class in the DataBaseConnector.

This is a Hibernate subclass that wraps any user defined data type. This way it can be persisted into the data base easly.

Version:
2.0
Author:
Juan A. Recio-García
